<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dr. M. Tamilkudimagan | Official Legacy Archive</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Official legacy website of Dr. M. Tamilkudimagan - Scholar, Speaker of the Assembly, and Minister.">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #FCF9F2; scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        h1, h2, h3 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }
        .bg-maroon { background-color: #4A0404; }
        .text-gold { color: #D4AF37; }
        .border-gold { border-color: #D4AF37; }
        .hero-gradient { background: linear-gradient(rgba(74, 4, 4, 0.9), rgba(74, 4, 4, 0.9)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599584449467-333066127160?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80'); background-size: cover; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-gray-900">

    <!-- Language Toggle/Top Bar -->
    <div class="bg-black text-white py-2 text-center text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">
        Official Digital Archive | <span class="text-gold">தமிழ் - English</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="p-6 flex justify-between items-center bg-white shadow-md sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold bg-maroon text-white px-3 py-1 italic">T.K.</div>
            <span class="font-bold text-maroon hidden sm:block">DR. M. TAMILKUDIMAGAN</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex space-x-6 font-semibold text-sm">
            <a href="#about" class="hover:text-gold transition">BIOGRAPHY</a>
            <a href="#achievements" class="hover:text-gold transition">LEGACY</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="bg-maroon text-white px-4 py-2 rounded">CONTACT</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="hero-gradient text-white py-32 px-6 relative">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
            <div class="md:w-3/5 space-y-8">
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-tight">A Life for <br><span class="text-gold italic underline">Tamil & The People.</span></h1>
                <p class="text-xl opacity-90 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">Honoring Dr. M. Tamilkudimagan (1939–2004). The Architect of Cultural Reforms, The Speaker of the 10th Assembly, and the Voice of Tamil Identity.</p>
                <div class="flex space-x-4 pt-4">
                    <a href="#about" class="bg-gold text-maroon font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-full hover:scale-105 transition transform">Explore Archive</a>
                    <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" class="border border-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-maroon transition">Read His Books</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/5 mt-12 md:mt-0 flex justify-center">
                <div class="relative group">
                    <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gold rounded-lg blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-100 transition duration-1000"></div>
                    <div class="relative w-80 h-96 bg-gray-200 border-4 border-white shadow-2xl overflow-hidden rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                        <!-- Replace with real image later -->
                        <span class="text-maroon font-bold p-10 text-center">Place Portrait of Dr. Tamilkudimagan Here</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Impact Bar -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white border-b">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 text-center">
            <div><h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-maroon">1989</h3><p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 mt-2">Speaker of the House</p></div>
            <div><h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-maroon">50+</h3><p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 mt-2">Literary Works</p></div>
            <div><h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-maroon">Minister</h3><p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 mt-2">Tamil Culture & HR&CE</p></div>
            <div><h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-maroon">PhD</h3><p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 mt-2">Scholarly Excellence</p></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="py-24 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <h2 class="text-4xl text-maroon">The Scholar-Statesman</h2>
                <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gold"></div>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed italic font-serif text-maroon">"I am a son of Tamil first, and a servant of the people second."</p>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Dr. Tamilkudimagan's journey from an academic scholar to the Speaker of the Tamil Nadu Legislative Assembly is a testament to his dedication. He championed the **Pure Tamil Movement** and worked tirelessly to ensure Tamil remained the heartbeat of administration and culture.</p>
                <a href="#" class="inline-block text-maroon font-bold border-b-2 border-gold pb-1 hover:text-gold transition">Read Full Biography →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-gray-100 h-64 rounded shadow-inner"></div>
                <div class="bg-maroon h-64 rounded shadow-lg flex items-end p-6">
                    <p class="text-white text-sm font-bold">Assembly Sessions, 1990</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Legacy / Achievements -->
    <section id="achievements" class="py-24 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
            <h2 class="text-5xl text-center text-maroon mb-16 underline decoration-gold">Landmark Contributions</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
                <!-- Card 1 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl transition-all border-t-8 border-maroon">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-6">🏛</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Legislative Discipline</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">As Speaker, he brought a scholarly dignity to the Assembly, ensuring debates were focused on policy and the welfare of Tamil Nadu.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Card 2 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl transition-all border-t-8 border-gold">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-6">✍️</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Literary Heritage</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Author of over 50 books, his works on politics, language, and the great leader Kalaignar remain essential reading.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Card 3 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl transition-all border-t-8 border-maroon">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-6">🛕</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Cultural Preservation</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">During his tenure as Minister, he revitalized the HR&CE department and prioritized the maintenance of historic Tamil temples.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section id="contact" class="py-24 bg-maroon text-white text-center px-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl mb-6">Support the Digital Archive</h2>
        <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 opacity-80 text-lg">We are looking for rare photographs, letters, and speeches of Dr. Tamilkudimagan to complete this history.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-4">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" class="px-6 py-4 rounded-full text-gray-900 w-full md:w-64 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gold outline-none">
            <button class="bg-gold text-maroon font-bold px-12 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-500 transition shadow-xl">Contact the Foundation</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-12 bg-white text-center border-t">
        <p class="text-maroon font-bold mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">The Dr. M. Tamilkudimagan Legacy Project</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm italic">"Valga Thamizh. Valga Thamizh Makkal."</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
